#

Ambrosia Apple Sandwich

10 min
$3.5
300 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 1

Allergens:

Peanuts

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Snack

Tags:

QuickHealthySnack

Description

A refreshing and crunchy apple sandwich filled with creamy peanut butter and topped with granola for a satisfying texture.

Ingredients

  • ambrosia apple: 1 large
  • peanut butter: 2 tablespoons
  • granola: 2 tablespoons
  • honey: 1 teaspoon
  • cinnamon: 1/2 teaspoon
